<inglise> COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 3389/81 of 27 November 1981 laying down detailed rules for export refunds in the wine sector </inglise>
<eesti> KOMISJONI M&Auml;&Auml;RUS (EM&Uuml;) nr 3389/81, millega s&auml;testatakse veinisektori eksporditoetuste &uuml;ksikasjalikud eeskirjad 27. november 1981 </eesti>
<inglise> THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES, </inglise>
<eesti> EUROOPA &Uuml;HENDUSTE KOMISJON, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to the Treaty establishing the European Economic Community, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse Euroopa Majandus&uuml;henduse asutamislepingut, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 337/79 of 5 February 1979 on the common organization of the market in wine (1), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 3456/80 (2), and in particular Article 20 (4) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 5. veebruari 1979. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust (EM&Uuml;) nr 337/79 veinituru &uuml;hise korralduse kohta, viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 3456/80, eriti selle artikli 20 l&otilde;iget 4, </eesti>
<inglise> Having regard to Council Regulation (EEC) No 345/79 of 5 February 1979 laying down general rules for granting export refunds on wine and criteria for fixing the amount of such refunds (3), as amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2009/81 (4), and in particular Article 6 (3) thereof, </inglise>
<eesti> v&otilde;ttes arvesse n&otilde;ukogu 5. veebruari 1979. aasta m&auml;&auml;rust nr 345/79, milles on kehtestatud veini eksporditoetuste andmise &uuml;ldeeskirjad ja toetussummade kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramise p&otilde;him&otilde;tted, viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2009/81, eriti selle artikli 6 l&otilde;iget 3, </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Commission Regulation (EEC) No 3002/76 of 10 December 1976 laying down detailed rules for export refunds in the wine sector (5), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 1619/81 (6), refers to Council Regulations which have since been consolidated; whereas in the interests of clarity and good administration that Regulation should also be consolidated; </inglise>
<eesti> ning arvestades, et: komisjoni 10. detsembri 1976. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 3002/76, milles on s&auml;testatud veinisektori eksporditoetuste &uuml;ksikasjalikud eeskirjad, viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1619/81, osutatakse n&otilde;ukogu m&auml;&auml;rustele, mis on sellest hetkest konsolideeritud; selguse ja t&otilde;husa haldamise huvides tuleks see m&auml;&auml;rus samuti konsolideerida; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 5 of Regulation (EEC) No 345/79 lays down that refunds are to be fixed periodically; whereas experience gained in respect of price trends in international trade shows that a six-month period is adequate; </inglise>
<eesti> m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 345/79 artiklis 5 on s&auml;testatud toetuste kindlaksm&auml;&auml;ramine korrap&auml;raste ajavahemike j&auml;rel; rahvusvahelises kaubanduses saadud kogemus hinnasuundumuste osas n&auml;itab, et kuuekuuline ajavahemik on piisav; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, at present, only concentrated grape must and table wines are eligible for refunds; </inglise>
<eesti> hetkel antakse toetust ainult kontsentreeritud viinamarjavirretele ja lauaveinidele; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas Article 1 (2) of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 3388/81 of 27 November 1981 laying down special detailed rules in respect of import and export licences in the wine sector (7) lays down that an export licence must be produced, if products in the wine sector are to qualify for an export refund; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjoni 27. novembri 1981. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3388/81 (milles on s&auml;testatud veinisektori impordi- ja ekspordilitsentside &uuml;ksikasjalikud erieeskirjad) artikli 1 l&otilde;ikes 2 s&auml;testatakse, et veinisektori toodete eksporditoetuse saamiseks tuleb esitada ekspordilitsents; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, however, the first indent of Article 5 (1) of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 3183/80 (8), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2646/81 (9), lays down that no licence shall be required for carrying out the operations referred to in Article 5 of Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2730/79 (10), as last amended by Regulation (EEC) No 2646/81; whereas Regulation (EEC) No 3388/81 furthermore lays down in Article 5 that no export licence is required for operations covering quantities below 30 hectolitres or, as the case may be, 3 000 kilograms; whereas it should accordingly be stated that the proof that export was carried out under a licence is not required for such operations; </inglise>
<eesti> komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3183/80 (viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2646/81) artikli 5 l&otilde;ike 1 esimese taandega on siiski s&auml;testatud, et komisjoni m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2730/79 (viimati muudetud m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 2646/81) artiklis 5 osutatud toimingute puhul ei n&otilde;uta mingit litsentsi; m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3388/81 artiklis 5 on lisaks sellele s&auml;testatud, et ekspordilitsentsi ei n&otilde;uta nende toimingute puhul, kus kogused on alla 30 hektoliitri v&otilde;i 3000 kilogrammi; vastavalt sellele tuleks m&auml;rkida, et selliste toimingute puhul ei n&otilde;uta t&otilde;endusmaterjale selle kohta, et eksport toimus litsentsi alusel; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas steps should be taken to ensure that table wines qualifying for refunds have the quality characteristics of table wines of the production region from which they come; </inglise>
<eesti> tuleks astuda samme, et tagada toetust saavate lauaveinide vastavus oma tootmispiirkonna lauaveinide kvaliteediomadustele; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas it should be laid down that the exporter must provide the necessary proof in order to obtain the refund; whereas, to this end, he should indicate inter alia the numbers and dates of the accompanying documents provided for by Commission Regulation (EEC) No 1153/75 (11), as last amended by the Act of Accession of Greece; whereas, however, pursuant to Article 13 (2) of that Regulation, the Member States may provide that the said document need not be drawn up for certain products in certain cases; whereas it is therefore necessary, to ensure effective supervision, to exclude the possibility of recourse to that provision in the context of the refund system; </inglise>
<eesti> tuleks s&auml;testada, et toetuse saamiseks peab eksportija esitama vajalikud t&otilde;endusmaterjalid; selleks peaks eksportija muu hulgas n&auml;itama komisjoni m&auml;&auml;rusega (EM&Uuml;) nr 1153/75 (viimati muudetud Kreeka &uuml;hinemisaktiga) ette n&auml;htud saatedokumentide numbrid ja kuup&auml;evad; vastavalt selle m&auml;&auml;ruse artikli 13 l&otilde;ikele 2 v&otilde;ivad liikmesriigid siiski s&auml;testada, et teatavatel juhtudel pole mainitud dokumente teatavate toodete puhul vaja koostada; seep&auml;rast on tulemuslikuks j&auml;relevalveks vaja v&auml;listada selle s&auml;tte kohaldamise v&otilde;imalus toetuss&uuml;steemi kontekstis; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas, however, in the case of deliveries for victualling ships and aircraft qualifying for refunds, it is not always easy to obtain the necessary documents in good time, particularly in non-producer Member States, on account of the difficulty of ascertaining the delivery dates in advance; whereas production of the required proof can thus represent a disproportionate burden in relation to the small quantities of table wines which normally make up such individual deliveries for traders who do not employ the procedure laid down in Article 26 of Regulation (EEC) No 2730/79 or in Council Regulation (EEC) No 565/80 of 4 March 1980 on the advance payment of export refunds in respect of agricultural products (1); whereas, for these small quantities, reference to the accompanying document may be sufficient to satisfy supervision requirements; </inglise>
<eesti> toetust saavate pardavarutarnete korral laevadele ja &otilde;hus&otilde;idukitele ei ole vajalike dokumentide &otilde;igeaegne hankimine alati lihtne, seda eriti liikmesriikides, mis ei tooda, sest tarnekuup&auml;evi on raske eelnevalt kindlaks teha; selliste lauaveinide &uuml;ksiktarnete v&auml;ikseid koguseid silmas pidades v&otilde;ib n&otilde;utavate t&otilde;endusmaterjalide esitamisest saada ebaproportsionaalselt suur koormus nende ettev&otilde;tjate jaoks, kes ei kasuta menetlusi, mis on s&auml;testatud m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2730/79 artiklis 26 v&otilde;i n&otilde;ukogu 4. m&auml;rtsi 1980. aasta m&auml;&auml;ruses (EM&Uuml;) nr 565/80 p&otilde;llumajandussaaduste ja -toodete eksporditoetuste ettemaksete kohta; selliste v&auml;ikeste koguste puhul v&otilde;ib viide saatedokumendile olla j&auml;relevalven&otilde;uete t&auml;itmiseks piisav; </eesti>
<inglise> Whereas the measures provided for in this Regulation are in accordance with the opinion of the Management Committee for Wine, </inglise>
<eesti> k&auml;esoleva m&auml;&auml;rusega etten&auml;htud meetmed on koosk&otilde;las veinituru korralduskomitee arvamusega, </eesti>
<inglise> HAS ADOPTED THIS REGULATION: </inglise>
<eesti> ON VASTU V&Otilde;TNUD K&Auml;ESOLEVA M&Auml;&Auml;RUSE. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 1 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 1 </eesti>
<inglise> Refunds shall be fixed at least once every six months. </inglise>
<eesti> Toetused m&auml;&auml;ratakse kindlaks v&auml;hemalt kord kuue kuu jooksul. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 2 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 2 </eesti>
<inglise> Except for supplies for the special purposes referred to in Article 5 of Regulation (EEC) No 2730/79 and supplies of the quantities referred to in Article 5 of Regulation (EEC) No 3388/81, the granting of refunds shall be conditional on production of proof that the products have been exported under an export licence. </inglise>
<eesti> V&auml;lja arvatud m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 2730/79 artiklis 5 osutatud eriotstarbeliste tarnete ja m&auml;&auml;ruse (EM&Uuml;) nr 3388/81 artiklis 5 osutatud tarnekoguste puhul on toetuste andmise tingimuseks, et tooted oleksid v&auml;lja veetud ekspordilitsentsi alusel. </eesti>
<inglise> Article 3 </inglise>
<eesti> Artikkel 3 </eesti>
<inglise> 1. </inglise>
<eesti> 1. </eesti>
<inglise> The granting of refunds shall be conditional upon proof that the products exported </inglise>
<eesti> Toetuste andmise tingimuseks on t&otilde;endusmaterjal selle kohta, et eksporditud toodetel </eesti>
<inglise> - were accompanied on export by an analysis certificate issued by an official body of the producer Member State or the exporting Member State certifying that they meet the Community quality standards for the products in question or, in the absence of such standards, the national standards applied by the exporting Member State, </inglise>
<eesti> - oli eksportimisel kaasas tootva liikmesriigi v&otilde;i eksportiva liikmesriigi ametiasutuse poolt v&auml;lja antud anal&uuml;&uuml;sit&otilde;end selle kohta, et tooted vastavad &uuml;henduse k&otilde;nealuste toodete kvaliteedistandarditele v&otilde;i selliste standardite puudumisel eksportivas liikmesriigis kohaldatavatele riiklikele standarditele, </eesti>
<inglise> and, in the case of table wine, </inglise>
<eesti> ja et lauaveinid, </eesti>
<inglise> - have been approved by a tasting committee recognized by the exporting Member State; where this Member State is not the producer, proof must also be provided that the wine in question is a Community table wine. </inglise>
<eesti> - on eksportiva liikmesriigi tunnustatud degusteerimiskomisjon heaks kiitnud; juhul kui k&otilde;nealune liikmesriik ei ole tootja, tuleb esitada t&otilde;endusmaterjal ka selle kohta, et k&otilde;nealune vein on &uuml;henduse lauavein. </eesti>
<inglise> The certificate referred to in the first indent of the first subparagraph shall mention at least the following: </inglise>
